'''塔博·姆武耶爾瓦·姆貝基'''<ref name="anc-bio1996">{{cite web|url=http://www.anc.org.za/ancdocs/history/mbeki/bio/ |title=Biography of Thabo Mbeki |publisher=ANC |author=Office of the Deputy Executive President |date=13 September 1996 |access-date=21 July 2007 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070711183712/http://www.anc.org.za/ancdocs/history/mbeki/bio/ |archivedate=11 July 2007}}</ref>（{{lang-xh|Thabo Mvuyelwa Mbeki}} {{IPA-xh|tʰaɓɔ mbɛːkʼi|}}，{{bd|1942年|6月18日|||catIdx=Mbeki}}），[[南非|南非]][[政治家|政治家]]，曾於1999年6月16日至2008年9月24日間擔任第2任[[南非總統|南非總統]]<ref name="gcis-profile2004">{{cite web|url=http://www.info.gov.za/leaders/president/index.htm |title=GCIS: profile information: Thabo Mvuyelwa Mbeki, Mr |publisher=GCIS |author=The Presidency |date=14 October 2004 |access-date=27 November 2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070416053536/http://www.info.gov.za/leaders/president/index.htm |archive-date=16 April 2007}}</ref><ref name="midnight">{{cite news|url=http://www.sabcnews.com/politics/government/0,2172,177349,00.html |title=Cabinet bids farewell to Mbeki |publisher=SABC news |date=25 September 2007 |access-date=25 September 2008 |quote=His resignation came into effect at midnight. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080929061212/http://www.sabcnews.com/politics/government/0,2172,177349,00.html |archive-date=29 September 2008 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2008年9月20日，在姆貝基的第二任期還有約九個月的時候，他在被{{le|非洲人國民大會全國執行委員會|National Executive Committee of the African National Congress}}召回後，宣布辭任南非總統一職<ref name="bbc2008-09-20">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/go/rss/-/2/hi/africa/7626646.stm |title=SA's Mbeki says he will step down |work=BBC News |date=20 September 2008 |access-date=21 September 2008 |location=London |archive-date=2021-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224151828/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/7626646.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此前，法官{{le|克里斯托弗·羅伯特·尼科爾森|Christopher Robert Nicholson|C·R·尼科爾森}}裁定，姆貝基政府起訴[[雅各布·祖瑪|雅各布·祖瑪]]涉嫌貪污等的行動均屬不當干預{{le|國家檢察機關|National Prosecuting Authority}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.news24.com/News24/South_Africa/News/0,,2-7-1442_2392604,00.html |title=Full Zuma Judgment |publisher=News24 |date=13 September 2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081031201836/http://www.news24.com/News24/South_Africa/News/0,,2-7-1442_2392604,00.html |archive-date=31 October 2008 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2009年1月12日，最高上訴法院一致推翻尼科爾森的判決<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mg.co.za/article/2009-01-12-judge-nicholson-redcarded-by-sca |title=Judge Nicholson Red-carded by SCA |publisher=Mail & Guardian Online |date=12 January 2009 |access-date=2020-01-05 |archive-date=2019-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191220043654/https://mg.co.za/article/2009-01-12-judge-nicholson-redcarded-by-sca |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mg.co.za/uploads/zumajudgement.pdf |title=National Director of Public Prosecutions v Zuma (573/08) [2009] ZASCA 1 (12 Jan 2009)|publisher=South African Supreme Court of Appeal |date=12 January 2009 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090320043142/http://www.mg.co.za/uploads/zumajudgement.pdf |archive-date=20 March 2009 |dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iol.co.za/index.php?from=rss_News&set_id=1&click_id=79&art_id=vn20090114050954196C745537 |title=Mbeki lashes out at lying politicians |publisher=IOL/The Star |date=14 January 2009}}</ref>，但辭職仍然生效。

